中国石化加油卡系统	加油站
system deployment, station operations
The fuel card system is utilized at the gas stations for managing refueling operations.

data.content:
中石化站级管理系统操作手册	加油站站长
manual usage, operational guidance
The manual is intended for use by station managers to understand and operate the station-level system.

加油卡	加油员

Fuel cards are used by attendants to process refueling transactions at the station.

加油机	黑名单

Fuel pumps check the black list to prevent service to blocked cards.<SEP>The black list is checked by fuel pumps to deny service to blocked cards.

Fuel pumps use the grey list to manage cards with transaction issues that need resolution.<SEP>Fuel pumps use the grey list to manage cards with unresolved transaction issues.

Station managers are responsible for overseeing the shift change process, ensuring smooth transitions.
